# Bidder Management API

Bidder Management is a simple API allowing consumers to perform CRUD operations on bidders.

## Bidders Collection [/bidders]

### Get All Bidders [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (array[Bidder])
    
    + Body
        
        [
          {
            "id": "e7fe51ce-4f63-7687-6353-ff0961c2eb0d",
            "name": "Bidder 1",
            "endpoint": "https://mybidder.com/bids",
            "state": "CREATED"
          },
          {
            "id": "d7f4f63e-c2cb-7687-c2cb-ff6353c2cb0e",
            "name": "Bidder 2",
            "endpoint": "https://test.bidder.com/bids",
            "state": "LIVE"
          },
          {
