### Get Bidder [GET /bidders/{id}]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Bidder)

### Update Bidder [PUT /bidders/{id}]

+ Request 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Bidder)
        + name: New Bidder Name

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Bidder)
        + name: New Bidder Name
    
# Data Structures

## Bidder (object)

+ id: `e7fe51ce-4f63-7687-6353-ff0961c2cb0d` (required, string) - The unique identifier for the bidder.
+ name: Bidder1 (required, string) - The human friendly name of the bidder.
+ endpoint: `https://mybidder.com/bids` (required, string) - The endpoint url that our exchange uses to send bid requests to this bidder.
+ state: `LIVE` (required, enum[string]) - The state of this bidder.
  + Members
    - CREATED
    - LIVE